                "content": "<div class='content'><b class='title'>Surah Al-Fatiha (The Introduction)</b>   <p class='text-center'><ar>بِـسْـمِ</ar> <ar>الـلّٰـهِ</ar> <ar>الرَّحْـمٰـنِ</ar> <ar>الرَّحِـيْمِ</ar></p> <ar>اَلْـحَمْدُ</ar> <ar>لِـلّٰـهِ</ar> <ar>رَبِّ</ar> <ar>الْـعٰلَمِـيْنَ</ar> <ar>﴿١﴾</ar> <ar>اَلرَّحْـمٰـنِ</ar> <ar>الرَّحِـيْمِ</ar> <ar>﴿٢﴾</ar> <ar>مـٰلِكِ</ar> <ar>يَـوْمِ</ar> <ar>الـدِّيْـنِ</ar> <ar>﴿٣﴾</ar> <ar>اِيَّـاكَ</ar> <ar>نَعْـبُدُ</ar> <ar>وَاِيَّـاكَ</ar> <ar>نَسْـتَـعِيْنُ</ar> <ar>﴿٤﴾</ar> <ar>اِهْدِنَا</ar> <ar>الصِّرَاطَ</ar> <ar>الْـمُسْتَــقِــيْمَ</ar> <ar>﴿٥﴾</ar> <ar>صِرَاطَ</ar> <ar>الَّـذِيْـنَ</ar> <ar>أَنْـعَمْتَ</ar> <ar>عَلَـيْـهِمْ</ar> <ar>﴿٦﴾</ar> <ar>غَـيْرِ</ar> <ar>الْـمَـغْضُوْبِ</ar> <ar>عَلَـيْـهِمْ</ar>  <ar>وَلَا</ar> <ar>الضَّآلِّیۡنَ</ar> <ar>﴿٧</ar> <gap></gap><b class='heading'>Pronunciation:</b> (1) Al hamdu lil-laahi rabbil alameen (2) Ar-Rahmanir- Raheem (3) Maaliki yaumid Deen (4) Iyyaaka na’abudu wa iyyaaka nasta’een (5) Ihdinas siraatal mustaqeem (6) Siraatal ladheena an ‘amta’ alaihim (7) Gairil mag-dhubi alaihim walad-daal-leen.  <gap></gap><b class='heading'>Meaning:</b>  (1) All praise be to Allah, the cherisher and sustainer of the worlds. (2) The most Gracious, the most Merciful. (3)  Master of the Day of Judgment. (4) Only You we worship and You we ask for help. (5) Show us the straightway. (6) The path of those upon whom You have bestowed favor. (7) Not of those who have evoked [Your] anger or of those who are astray. </div> <div class='words-container'> <b class='title'> Literally Meaning </b> <div class='split-words-container'> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اَلْحَمْدُ </span> <span class='split-en'> All praise </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> لِلّٰهِ </span> <span class='split-en'> (for Allah) be to Allah </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> رَبِّ </span> <span class='split-en'> the cherisher and sustainer (Lord) </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الْعٰلَمِيْنَ </span> <span class='split-en'> of the worlds </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الرَّحْمٰنِ </span> <span class='split-en'> the most Gracious </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الرَّحِيْمِ </span> <span class='split-en'> the most Merciful </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> مٰلِكِ </span> <span class='split-en'> Master </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> يَوْمِ </span> <span class='split-en'> the day </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الدِّيْنِ </span> <span class='split-en'> (of) Judgment </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> إِيَّا </span> <span class='split-en'> Only </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> كَ </span> <span class='split-en'> (of) You </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> نَعْبُدُ </span> <span class='split-en'> we worship </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> وَ </span> <span class='split-en'> and </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> إِيَّا </span> <span class='split-en'> only </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> كَ </span> <span class='split-en'> You </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> نَسْتَعِيْنُ </span> <span class='split-en'> we ask for help </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اِهْدِ </span> <span class='split-en'> show </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> نَا </span> <span class='split-en'> us </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الصِّرَاطَ </span> <span class='split-en'> way </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الْمُسْتَقِيْمَ </span> <span class='split-en'> the straight </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> صِّرَاطَ </span> <span class='split-en'> the path </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الَّذِيْنَ </span> <span class='split-en'> those </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> أَنْعَمْتَ </span> <span class='split-en'> You have bestowed favor/ favuor </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> عَلَيْ </span> <span class='split-en'> upon </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> هِمْ </span> <span class='split-en'> them </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> غَيْرِ </span> <span class='split-en'> except </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الْمَغْضُوْبِ </span> <span class='split-en'> who have evoked anger </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> عَلَيْ </span> <span class='split-en'> upon </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> هِمْ </span> <span class='split-en'> them </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> وَ </span> <span class='split-en'> and </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> لَا </span> <span class='split-en'> not (of those) </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> الضَّآلِّيْنَ </span> <span class='split-en'> who are astray </span> </p> </div> </div>"
