                "title": "Duaa For Deceased Person (Female Child)  ",
                "content": "<div class='content'><b class='title'>Duaa For Deceased Person (Female Child) </b><gap></gap>   <ar>اَللّٰهُمَّ</ar> <ar>اجْعَلْهَا</ar> <ar>لَنَا</ar> <ar>فَرْطًا</ar> <ar>وَّ</ar> <ar>اجْعَلْهَا</ar> <ar>لَنَا</ar> <ar>لَنَاأَجْرًاوَّ</ar> <ar>اجْعَلْهَا</ar> <ar>لَنَا</ar> <ar>ذُخْرًا</ar> <ar>وَّ</ar> <ar>اجْعَلْهَا</ar> <ar>لَنَا</ar> <ar>شَافِعًةً</ar> <ar>وَّ</ar> <ar>مُشَفَّعًةً</ar>  <gap></gap><b class='heading'>Pronunciation:</b> Alla Hum-Maj Alha Lana Farataw Waj Alha Lana Ajraw Wa Jhukhuraw WajAl-ha Lana Shaafi Aw Wa Mushaffaa  <gap></gap><b class='heading'>Meaning:</b> Oh! Allah, make her (this child) for our means of preservation and make her a source of reward and treasure for us and make her a pleader for us and one whose pleading is accepted. (Bukhari (I.F. BD) H-1254, Mishkat H-1690) </div> <div class='words-container'> <b class='title'> Literally Meaning </b> <div class='split-words-container'> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اَللّٰهُمَّ </span> <span class='split-en'> Oh! Allah </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اجْعَلْ </span> <span class='split-en'> make </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> هَا </span> <span class='split-en'> her (this child) </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> لَنَا </span> <span class='split-en'> for us </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> فَرْطًا </span> <span class='split-en'> preservation </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> وَّ </span> <span class='split-en'> and </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اجْعَلْهَا </span> <span class='split-en'> make her </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> لَنَا </span> <span class='split-en'> for us </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> ذُخْرًا </span> <span class='split-en'> a source of reward and treasure for us </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> وَّ </span> <span class='split-en'> and </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> اجْعَلْهَا </span> <span class='split-en'> make her </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> لَنَا </span> <span class='split-en'> for us </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> شَافِعًةً </span> <span class='split-en'> pleader </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> وَّ </span> <span class='split-en'> And </span> </p> <p class='split-word'> <span class='split-ar'> مُشَفَّعًةً </span> <span class='split-en'> whose pleading is accepted </span> </p> </div> <div class='content'><b class='title'>After 4 th  Takbir, End The Salaat Through Salaam</div></div>"
